{
  "name": "cherry-markdown-next-vsc",
  "displayName": "Cherry Markdown Next VSC",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "VS Code / Cursor extension for Cherry Markdown Next",
  "publisher": "ankio",
  "license": "MIT",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/AnkioTomas/cherry-markdown-next-vsc.git"
  },
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.125.0"
  },
  "main": "./dist/extension.js",
  "activationEvents": [
    "onCustomEditor:cherry-markdown-next.editor"
  ],
  "contributes": {
    "customEditors": [
      {
        "viewType": "cherry-markdown-next.editor",
        "displayName": "Cherry Markdown",
        "selector": [
          {
            "filenamePattern": "*.md"
          }
        ],
        "priority": "default"
      }
    ],
    "configuration": [
      {
        "id": "cherryMarkdownNext.ui",
        "title": "界面",
        "order": 1,
        "properties": {
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ui.layout": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "split",
              "edit",
              "preview"
            ],
            "default": "split",
            "order": 1,
            "scope": "resource",
            "enumDescriptions": [
              "编辑区与预览区并排",
              "仅编辑区",
              "仅预览区"
            ],
            "markdownDescription": "初始布局模式。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ui.theme": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "default",
              "github",
              "claude",
              "morandi",
              "latex",
              "vue",
              "notion"
            ],
            "default": "default",
            "order": 2,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "编辑器主题 id（需已在 webview 中加载对应主题 CSS）。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ui.statusbar": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true,
            "order": 3,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "显示底部状态栏。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ui.sidebar": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true,
            "order": 4,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "显示侧边栏。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ui.lineNumbers": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true,
            "order": 5,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "编辑区显示行号。"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "cherryMarkdownNext.files",
        "title": "文件处理",
        "order": 2,
        "properties": {
          "cherryMarkdownNext.upload.mode": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "off",
              "local",
              "script",
              "picgo",
              "upic"
            ],
            "default": "off",
            "order": 1,
            "scope": "resource",
            "enumDescriptions": [
              "禁用粘贴/拖入上传（不注册 Cherry `onParseFile`）",
              "保存到文档旁目录（默认 assets/），写入相对路径",
              "调用本地脚本上传（Typora Custom Command 约定）",
              "调用 PicGo 桌面端 / picgo-core CLI",
              "调用 macOS uPic CLI"
            ],
            "markdownDescription": "粘贴或拖入图片/文件时的处理方式（Cherry `onParseFile`）。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.upload.directory": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "assets",
            "order": 2,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "`local` 模式：相对文档目录的保存路径。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.upload.script": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 3,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "`script` 模式：可执行上传脚本路径（绝对路径，或相对工作区/文档目录）。扩展只追加图片路径参数，不代拼解释器。\n\n兼容 Typora：成功时 stdout 首行为 `http(s)` URL；失败时 stdout 输出错误文本。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.upload.picgoPath": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 4,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "`picgo` 模式：PicGo 可执行文件路径。留空则自动探测（macOS `/Applications/PicGo.app/...`，或 PATH 中的 `picgo`）。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.upload.upicPath": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 5,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "`upic` 模式：uPic 可执行文件路径。留空则使用 `/Applications/uPic.app/Contents/MacOS/uPic`。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.upload.timeoutMs": {
            "type": "number",
            "default": 60000,
            "minimum": 1000,
            "order": 6,
            "scope": "resource",
            "markdownDescription": "CLI / 脚本上传超时（毫秒）。"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "cherryMarkdownNext.ai",
        "title": "AI",
        "order": 3,
        "properties": {
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.enabled": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": false,
            "order": 1,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "启用 AI 工具栏（润色 / 校对 / 翻译 / 摘要 / 自定义）。仅支持 OpenAI 兼容 Chat Completions。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.provider": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "openai",
              "openrouter",
              "deepseek",
              "moonshot",
              "ollama",
              "custom"
            ],
            "default": "openai",
            "order": 2,
            "scope": "window",
            "enumDescriptions": [
              "OpenAI / ChatGPT（api.openai.com）",
              "OpenRouter（openrouter.ai）",
              "DeepSeek（api.deepseek.com）",
              "Moonshot Kimi（api.moonshot.cn）",
              "Ollama 本地（127.0.0.1:11434）",
              "自定义 OpenAI 兼容地址（需填写 endpoint）"
            ],
            "markdownDescription": "AI 供应商预设。内置供应商自动填 endpoint 与默认模型；选 `custom` 时必须配置 `endpoint`。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.endpoint": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 3,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "Chat Completions 完整 URL。留空则使用供应商预设；非空时覆盖预设（适合代理 / 私有部署）。\n\n例：`https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions`"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.apiKey": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 4,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "API Key（写入 `Authorization: Bearer ...`）。**会进入 settings.json**，共享环境更推荐用 `apiKeyEnv`。Ollama 通常可留空。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.apiKeyEnv": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 5,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "从环境变量读取 API Key（`apiKey` 为空时生效）。例：`OPENAI_API_KEY`、`DEEPSEEK_API_KEY`、`OPENROUTER_API_KEY`。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.model": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 6,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "模型名称。留空则使用供应商默认（如 `gpt-4o-mini`、`deepseek-chat`、`openai/gpt-4o-mini`）。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.temperature": {
            "type": "number",
            "default": -1,
            "minimum": -1,
            "maximum": 2,
            "order": 7,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "采样温度。`-1` 表示按动作使用内置默认（校对偏低、润色略高）；`0`–`2` 则统一覆盖。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.headers": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "default": {},
            "order": 8,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "额外 HTTP 头。若已含 `Authorization`，则不再自动附加 Bearer。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.timeoutMs": {
            "type": "number",
            "default": 120000,
            "minimum": 1000,
            "order": 9,
            "scope": "window",
            "markdownDescription": "AI 请求超时（毫秒）。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.prompt.polish": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 10,
            "scope": "window",
            "editPresentation": "multiline",
            "markdownDescription": "「智能润色」system 提示词。**留空使用内置**；填写后整段替换内置提示（请自行写清输出约束）。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.prompt.proofread": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 11,
            "scope": "window",
            "editPresentation": "multiline",
            "markdownDescription": "「纠错校对」system 提示词。**留空使用内置**；填写后整段替换。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.prompt.translate": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 12,
            "scope": "window",
            "editPresentation": "multiline",
            "markdownDescription": "「翻译文本」system 提示词。**留空使用内置**；填写后整段替换。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.prompt.summarize": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 13,
            "scope": "window",
            "editPresentation": "multiline",
            "markdownDescription": "「生成摘要」system 提示词。**留空使用内置**；填写后整段替换。"
          },
          "cherryMarkdownNext.ai.prompt.custom": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "",
            "order": 14,
            "scope": "window",
            "editPresentation": "multiline",
            "markdownDescription": "「自定义」system 提示词。**留空使用内置**；填写后整段替换。用户对话框指令仍通过 user 消息传入。"
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "scripts": {
    "vscode:prepublish": "pnpm run build",
    "build": "vite build && vite build --config vite.webview.config.ts",
    "watch": "vite build --watch",
    "watch:webview": "vite build --config vite.webview.config.ts --watch",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit",
    "package": "vsce package --no-dependencies --out dist/cherry-markdown-next-vsc.vsix"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^22.20.0",
    "@types/vscode": "^1.125.0",
    "@vscode/vsce": "^3.9.2",
    "typescript": "^5.9.3",
    "vite": "8.0.5"
  },
  "private": true,
  "dependencies": {
    "cherry-markdown-next": "^0.1.3"
  }
}
